Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.42,0:13:03.55,Asteroid - Book2,,0,0,0,,{\org(654,656)\frz9.374\pos(604,588)}欣賞天然石的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.30,Asteroid - Book1,,0,0,0,,{\org(586,449)\frz15.99\pos(538,437)}生日石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.30,Asteroid - Book2,,0,0,0,,{\org(654,656)\frz15.99\pos(606,632)}欣賞天然石的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,生日石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.12,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是按順序介紹的話就能寫十二回了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.50,0:13:05.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,太天真了  夢露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:11.75,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也有按每天算的生日石  竟然能寫366回連載文章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:13.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,學姐好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.57,0:13:15.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,看來留級興致勃勃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:20.90,Asteroid - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs80\pos(744,557)\frz15.66\c&H9E959D&}主題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家都確定了主題  好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.85,0:13:20.82,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈不是要寫小行星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,雖然是這樣想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.42,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,要是有人看了我的文章產生了興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.60,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,比我們先找到了小行星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:31.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好痛苦  好不甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.72,0:13:34.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我想應該沒事的  畢竟這事比較硬核
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,總之主題是決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:39.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈  那是作業嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:43.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是  是社團活動用的文章
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.55,0:13:44.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,行文會不會怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.77,0:13:47.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.22,0:13:50.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.85,0:13:54.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  太過於說明和解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,真是的  就是科普文章  這沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:59.15,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,文章太過於普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,讓讀者無法感覺到米菈你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:09.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我們學生會的會刊  也會在文筆和表達方式上好好斟酌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.95,0:14:16.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就算你對我說這麼多  我也不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:16.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.75,0:14:27.80,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這是米菈不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:30.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,向別人聽取意見自己卻中途逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:35.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,人家這麼努力的成果就這樣被否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.00,0:14:38.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,也不是不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:42.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米莎姐雖然當學生會長時做事很嚴格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:45.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不過卻意外地不太會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.32,0:14:49.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,但多虧這個  我和米莎姐的聊天終於有進展了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.87,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.001\move(1142,328,1212,452,26,4989)}要怎麼做才會原諒我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.87,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.001\move(1050,178,1114,302,0,4989)}讓米菈不開心了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:51.87,Asteroid - Chat,,0,0,0,,{\frz7.352\move(1242,634,1312,750,0,4989)}那可真是不妙啊  米菈說了些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:52.02,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,簡直是天上掉餡餅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,小鈴  你都說出聲了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:54.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.42,0:14:58.55,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,原以為會很順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:01.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,大家最初不都這樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我第一次做的麵包就沒有被採用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.65,0:15:06.85,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是不好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.27,0:15:10.07,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,不是  說是太沒品了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.05,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是胖次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:17.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,是藍髮來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:21.52,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說是在找用在文章上的圖片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:22.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.27,0:15:25.35,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,就當是轉換心情  米菈來畫怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,以前不是挺喜歡畫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.52,0:15:31.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,說是要用於介紹木星和它的衛星  類似希臘神話的畫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.77,0:15:33.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.12,0:15:35.37,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,希臘神話？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.90,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,希臘神話和星星之間有著很多聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.77,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好像很有趣  我也讀讀看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.32,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:44.25,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.80,0:15:46.67,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,發送
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.50,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,如果報道也像這樣刷刷地寫完就輕鬆了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:54.10,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.87,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈幫我畫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.22,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.22,0:16:06.57,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝你  特別可愛的插圖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:07.72,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:08.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,多虧你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.65,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.87,0:16:10.47,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.92,Asteroid - text,,0,0,0,,米菈選了漫畫的形式啊
